downloadDescription: This download contains content for Project 2002 that has been retired from TechNet. The content you requested has already retired. It's available to download on this page.
detailsSection: This download contains content for Project 2002, including planning, deployment, maintenance, resource kit, and training courseware, that has been retired from TechNet.
systemRequirementsSection:
Windows 2000 Professional
Windows XP Professional or later
installInstructionSection:
1. The download is a pdf file. To start the download, click Download.
  2. If the File Download dialog box appears, do one of the following:
    • To start the download immediately, click Open.
    • To copy the download to your computer to view at a later time, click Save.
